	</VanillaRacesExpandedInsector.GenelineGeneDef>
	<VanillaRacesExpandedInsector.GenelineGeneDef ParentName="VRE_MutationGene">
		<defName>VRE_EcdysoneOverdrive</defName>
		<label>ecdysone overdrive</label>
		<description>Carriers of this gene experience an ecdysone overdrive, creating a constant need for kill satiety. Prolonged periods without melee kills inflict increasing mood penalties, driving them towards violent confrontations to maintain their mental balance.</description>
